  "name": "Scout Squad",
  "titles": "Scout Squad",
  "lore": "Scouts are equipped with lighter recon armour, which affords them far greater mobility than a full suit of power armour and allows them to operate far ahead of the main Space Marine advance. These bold warriors are often some of the most experienced warriors in a Legion’s line companies and specialise in disrupting enemy advances, and marking enemy positions. In battle, these agile warriors take to the high ground to ply their skills as snipers, or race ahead of the main advance to perform daring assaults on objectives, holding them until slower troops can relieve them.",
